Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}（綺羅羅）バレたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}（綺羅羅）攻めるでしょ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,（パンダ）ぬっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,（伏黒）パンダ先輩!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,（パンダ）大丈夫だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,問題ない!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,伏黒!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,★を探せ!!
