Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:12.02,Ruby,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(702,1028)}ほし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}予め 誰かしらの呪力を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:13.61,Ruby,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(650,936)}あらかじ
